{
  "stem": "19895.6",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And the barrels somehow gave away to me when I was at the bottom of the steps, they-- they moved.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "People apparently were under the barrels and behind the barrels.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And I went behind some barrel and it was semi-dark there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I saw a person just quietly being there and showing quiet and I was very quiet.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And then in couple of hours, looking through the cracks of the door, we seen some strange uniformed people chasing some German uniformed people with their arms up in the air.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And at that point, one of the barrel moves away, opens up, and the woman who gave me the chocolate piece and coins gets out.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And as I recall her identity as I seen her, she was a very courageous Russian spy who spoke German language and was a woman who was hiding her identity with the German soldiers.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And in her drunkness that night, she not knowing what she's saying, she revealed that she speaks Russian to me.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And that woman immediately directed the Russians down to the cellar.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And the Russians came in with-- with their machine guns.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And it happens that in the cellar were at least 15, 18 people, half of them German soldiers who were hiding and giving up and they wanted to be captured.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Some of them were Arrow Cross people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And myself, and maybe two other, were Jews like myself, who didn't go away with the evacuation of the camp.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And I was freed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "I was freed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And-- and the war went on.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't care the German soldiers' name.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the two other people who were there, they didn't care about me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Everybody was trying to find out what happened to-- is anybody else in the camp alive, and so on.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
